# Backend tests

When working on backend tests, on `apps/backend/vitest.config.ts`, or on backend source under `apps/backend/src/{services,controllers,routes,app.ts}`, read and follow the project skill at `.cursor/skills/backend/testing/SKILL.md`.

That skill is the source of truth for backend test layout, supertest usage, what to cover per service / route, and required tests when adding new backend features. Do not write backend tests that conflict with it unless the user explicitly overrides it in the same conversation.
